Package org.echo.mobile.framework.model.contract.input

  • Interface Summary 
    Interface Description
    EncodingContext
    Describes context of current encoding process
    InputValueType
    Describes base functionality of contract input parameter model type
  • Class Summary 
    Class Description
    AccountAddressInputValueType
    Implementation of interface InputValueType for account address types. Can encode addresses with account prefix "1.2." and without it.
    AddressInputValueType
    Implementation of interface InputValueType for any address types. Can encode only prefixed addresses. For example, account address: 1.2.1. If address is not clear, throws exception.
    BooleanInputValueType
    Extension of interface InputValueType for boolean type
    BytesInputValueType
    Implementation of interface InputValueType for bytes types
    ContractAddressInputValueType
    Implementation of interface InputValueType for contract address types. Can decode addresses with contract prefix "1.14." and without it.
    ContractInputEncoder
    Encodes input contract data according to required input types types
    DynamicArrayInputValueType
    Implementation of interface InputValueType for dynamic arrays
    DynamicStringArrayValueType
    Implementation of interface InputValueType for dynamic string array
    EthContractAddressInputValueType
    Implementation of interface InputValueType for ethereum contract address types.
    FixedArrayInputValueType
    Implementation of interface InputValueType for fixed arrays
    FixedBytesInputValueType
    Implementation of interface InputValueType for fixed bytes types
    InputValue
    Describes value value and it's type type of contract method parameter
    InputValueTypeKt  
    NumberInputValueType
    Implementation of interface InputValueType for number types
    StringInputValueType
    Implementation of interface InputValueType for string types
